casebody.data:
Kenneth FERNANDES, petitioner,
v.
CARNIVAL CORPORATION, dba Carnival Cruise Lines, Inc. No. 12-456. Supreme Court of the United States April 15, 2013.

Motion of Port Ministries International for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
